            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Extremely disappointed with the management of this school. The security staff behaves rudely with parents, and when concerns are raised, the management doesn't even bother to respond.\n\nThe disbursal process is a complete mess—there is no proper communication, timings are not followed, and parents are left waiting outside in harsh weather conditions. When I questioned the security in-charge about the inconsistent disbursal timings, he not only refused to provide a proper answer but also misbehaved and scolded us. Shockingly, he even told us to find another school if we had a problem. This is unacceptable behavior from someone responsible for student safety.\n\nDespite raising these concerns via email, the school management has completely ignored them. No acknowledgment, no resolution—just silence. This shows a complete lack of accountability and respect for parents who have trusted this institution for years.\n\nIf this is how they treat parents, I can’t imagine how they handle internal issues. Extremely poor management, zero professionalism, and no regard for parents' concerns. Would NOT recommend this school to anyone who expects basic respect and proper communication.",
