          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "1",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "Very bad school - unnecessary pressure created on students, class 9 students are given questions of Class 12 and IIT Advance. There is a Physics Teacher, who simply torchures students by teaching them topics beyond their ICSE Syllabus and even the Physics Question Format is not as per ICSE Syllabus. The instructions given in English question papers are always confusing. They keep two papers on each day and with almost negligible study leaves, they are always in a hurry to conduct the Half Yearly and Annual Exam and then students are not taught anything in the month after the exams, even syllabus is given late. I am literally fed up. Their science and maths teachers are not worthy at all. Coming to extracurricular activities, in Cricket and Football, higher class students select their juniors and the particular sports teacher is always non vigilante and not present observing students. English speaking is not mandatory and students roam in the school talking in Hindi. The management is not controlling Bullies and a lot of bullying happens.",
